OL,5,Cschool pupil
OL,7,FA young man has accused the ex-
OL,8,Fbroadcaster Huw Edwards of
OL,9,Finappropriate behaviour towards him
OL,10,Fwhen he was a sixth-form student.
OL,12,FHuw Edwards, 63, sent suggestive
OL,13,Fmessages to the young man, who was 18
OL,14,Fat the time, and invited him for a
OL,15,Fvisit at the BBC's headquarters in
OL,16,FLondon.
OL,18,FEmyr, not his real name, alleges Huw
OL,19,FEdwards of grooming behaviour.
