OL,7,FThe former BBC News at Ten presenter
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to making indecent
OL,9,Fimages of children in September 2024.
OL,11,FThese new allegations by the young man
OL,12,Fare not associated with the criminal
OL,13,Fcase.
OL,15,FSpeaking for the first time and
OL,16,Fanonymously on S4C's current affairs
OL,17,Fprogramme, Y Byd ar Bedwar, Emyr said:
OL,18,F"People like him believe they can do
OL,19,Fwhatever they want, and abuse their
OL,20,Fpower."
