OL,7,FThey first met at a community concert
OL,8,Fwhere Huw Edwards was the compere, and
OL,9,FEmyr was performing in his school
OL,10,Funiform.
OL,12,F"He came up to me at the end of the
OL,13,Fnight to say hello. He said that the
OL,14,Fperformance was good, that I was very
OL,15,Ftalented and that he wanted to connect
OL,16,Fwith me."
OL,18,FHe alleges that Edwards told him to
OL,19,Ffollow him on Instagram and that he
OL,20,Fcould help him with his music career.
