OL,7,F"He asked me if I wanted to meet him
OL,8,Fin London and have a tour of the BBC,
OL,9,Fwhere I could meet a few contacts."
OL,11,FEmyr says that he accepted the
OL,12,Finvitation and was taken around the
OL,13,Fnewsroom by Edwards, where he says he
OL,14,Fwas introduced to his colleagues as a
OL,15,F"friend" who had a "musical talent".
OL,17,FHe says he was promised opportunities
OL,18,Fto perform at concerts in London, but
OL,19,Fthis never happened.
