OL,7,FDuring this time, they would also
OL,8,Fspeak on Instagram; a platform later
OL,9,Frevealed in Edwards' court case to be
OL,10,Fa forum he would use to boost his low
OL,11,Fself-esteem.
OL,13,FIn those messages, the broadcaster,
OL,14,Fwho is almost 40 years older than
OL,15,FEmyr, would often use kisses and
OL,16,Fhearts in his messages, as well as
OL,17,Fcalling him "babe" and "big boy".
