OL,7,FAt the time, Emyr thought that
OL,8,FEdwards' was being "banterous", but
OL,9,Fupon reflection, he now sees their
OL,10,Fcommunication as inappropriate.
OL,12,F"He was trying to flirt. It was some
OL,13,Fsort of grooming communication."
OL,15,FAfter a few months, Emyr says the
OL,16,Fmessages between them stopped and Huw
OL,17,FEdwards unfollowed him.
OL,19,F"He just lost interest in me. I don't
OL,20,Fthink I gave him what he was looking
OL,21,Ffor," he said.
