OL,7,FEmyr now questions whether Huw
OL,8,FEdwards' former employer, the BBC, had
OL,9,Fenough checks in place to protect him
OL,10,Fwhen he visited the company's building
OL,11,Fwith the presenter.
OL,13,F"Just because I was with Huw Edwards,
OL,14,FI could walk in without a problem. I
OL,15,Fdon't remember anyone asking me why I
OL,16,Fwas there.
OL,18,F"There should be some sort of
OL,19,Fprocedure or professional reason for
OL,20,Fsomeone to enter the building."
