OL,7,FThe BBC said: "We have been clear that
OL,8,Fwe are appalled by Huw Edwards'
OL,9,Fcrimes. He has betrayed not just the
OL,10,FBBC, but audiences who put their trust
OL,11,Fin him.
OL,13,F"A Board-commissioned independent
OL,14,Freview of the BBC's workplace culture
OL,15,Fis currently underway, with a
OL,16,Fparticular focus on preventing abuse
OL,17,Fof power and ensuring everyone at the
OL,18,FBBC conducts themselves in line with
OL,19,Four values.
